---
import StoryStep from '../StoryStep.astro';
import Canvas from '../Canvas.astro';
// import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
// import Item from '../Item.astro';
// cut-out imports go here when assets are ready
---

<StoryStep title="Sounds of Atlanta" mediaFirst>
	<Canvas slot="media" fill fitScale class="cluster">
		{/* drop <Item><Image …/></Item> cut-outs here, position with ?edit */}
	</Canvas>

	<div class="copy">
		<p>
			Atlanta always had the roots—the gospel, the churches, the Auburn Avenue
			clubs. But it was never a music capital. Memphis had Stax; Atlanta had
			potential.
		</p>
		<p>
			Then, in the 1990s, it stopped waiting its turn. OutKast rewrote what rap
			could be. LaFace built R&B empires. Trap was born here and became the
			default language of pop. The women ran it too—from TLC, the best-selling
			girl group in U.S. history, to today's chart-toppers.
		</p>
	</div>
</StoryStep>

<style>
	/* breathing room below the body text, before the prev/next bar */
	.copy {
		padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	/* more gap between the canvas and the copy on phone */
	:global(:root[data-bp='phone']) .copy {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}
</style>
